1. *Shvatim* da je to teško razumeti. (I understand that it's hard to comprehend.)
2. On je shvatio situaciju. (He understood the situation.)
3. Ona je shvatila da je pogrešila. (She realized that she was wrong.)
4. *Shvatili* smo da je to bila greška. (We realized that it was a mistake.)
5. Oni ga nisu *shvatili*. (They didn't get him.)